data.title: Princesse Tam-Tam, Lyon
data.meta_description: Princesse Tam-Tam is where young ladies go to get original and modern underwear at reasonable prices. Selections come in various colors and shapes. From soft lace to plant or fruit patterned ensembles, every pieces will emphasize your fresh and happy look. Besides lingerie, you'll also find fascinating night clothing, robes and swim wear in unique textures and materials. The swimsuits are exquisite and come in pastel or bright colors. Check their website for more details.
